race.comment: LAYTON MAGIC (8) recorded his 2nd career win last time at this track, scoring by 0.8 lengths (22.54). Can continue on with his winning form. NO CENTS (1) recorded her 4th career win last time out (29.66) at The Gardens after drawing the inside. Missed the frame only look here. Boasts two wins from two starts out of this box. Capable of going well again. DESPICABLE DASH (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with four wins and two minors from 10 tries. Was out of the placings last time (17.83) at Richmond Straight in a Grade 3/4, finishing fourth and beaten 6 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. BEAUTIFUL MAGPIE (6) will be hard to beat despite making her debut at this circuit.
